<!-- ============================================================
  THE CHALLENGE (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>A 35-Year Legacy Brand Being Outpaced by New-Age Online Jewellery Platforms</h2>
        <p>
          Gujarat Gems had been a fixture on Ring Road, Surat since 1990. Three generations of customers had walked in, bought gold ornaments, diamond sets, and loose gemstones based purely on personal trust and word-of-mouth. The store had excellent craftsmen, genuine products, and decades of goodwill.
        </p>
        <p>
          But the Kothari family noticed something troubling over the past two to three years. Younger buyers in their twenties and thirties were not walking in the way older customers did. Instead, they were buying from BlueStone, CaratLane, and Tanishq's online store because those platforms made jewellery browsing effortless. Gujarat Gems had no website, no Instagram shop, and no way for someone in Mumbai or Bangalore to discover them and purchase online.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mehul Kothari, the managing partner, reached out to us after his daughter pointed out that searching "gold jewellery Surat" on Google showed none of their store's listings. A competitor with inferior craftsmanship was ranking first. That was the moment they decided the business needed a digital presence built properly, not just a brochure website.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-challenge-list">
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No e-commerce presence at all</strong>
              <p>No website, no online catalogue, no way for out-of-city buyers to browse or purchase products</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>High-value product trust problem</strong>
              <p>Jewellery buyers spend ₹20,000 to ₹5 lakh per order and need strong trust signals before purchasing from an unknown online store</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Competitors dominating local search</strong>
              <p>Established online brands and local competitors with basic websites were ranking for every relevant search term in Surat</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No digital payment or EMI infrastructure</strong>
              <p>High-ticket jewellery purchases need Razorpay integration with EMI options for buyers who want to spread payments across 3 to 12 months</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  OUR APPROACH (dark bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label light">Our Approach</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>Build Trust First, Then Build Traffic.</h2>
        <p>
          For high-value jewellery, trust is the product. Before we wrote a single line of code, we spent time understanding Gujarat Gems' customer base, their best-selling product categories, the average order value, and what made buyers choose them over larger brands. Every design and marketing decision came from that foundation.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-process-steps">
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">01</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Product Catalogue and Photography Brief</h4>
              <p>Worked with the Gujarat Gems team to catalogue 200+ products across gold ornaments, diamond jewellery, and loose gemstones. Created a photography brief specifying angles, background, and resolution so every product image conveyed quality and authenticity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">02</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Custom Shopify Store with Jewellery Theme</h4>
              <p>Built a Shopify store with a custom theme designed specifically for high-value jewellery. Clean layouts, large product images, metal and stone filter options, and trust badges on every product page: BIS hallmark, purity certification, and 30-day return policy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">03</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Razorpay Integration with EMI Options</h4>
              <p>Integrated Razorpay with zero-cost EMI for purchases above ₹10,000 across all major banks. COD option for orders under ₹5,000. Enabled UPI, credit card, debit card, and net banking to remove all payment friction at checkout.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">04</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Google Shopping and Search Campaigns</h4>
              <p>Launched Google Shopping campaigns targeting buyers searching for gold jewellery, diamond sets, and gemstones in Surat and across Gujarat. Search campaigns targeted high-intent keywords. Retargeting campaigns brought back visitors who viewed products but did not purchase.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">05</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Instagram Shopping and Local SEO</h4>
              <p>Set up Instagram Shopping so products could be purchased directly from posts and reels. Optimised Google Business Profile for "jewellery shop Ring Road Surat," built local citations, and created product-specific pages targeting Surat and South Gujarat buyers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  WHAT WE BUILT (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label">Deliverables</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>Everything Delivered, Nothing Left Half Done</h2>
        <p>
          The full project scope was defined in writing before any work began. Here is exactly what was delivered within the 8-week timeline.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-deliverables-grid">
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛍️</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Custom Shopify Store (200+ Products)</h4>
              <p>Fully custom Shopify theme with category pages for gold ornaments, diamond jewellery, and loose gemstones. Metal purity and weight filters on every category page for easy browsing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">💳</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Razorpay + COD Integration</h4>
              <p>Complete payment gateway setup with zero-cost EMI for purchases above ₹10,000. All major payment methods enabled. COD configured for eligible pin codes in Surat and Ahmedabad.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛒</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Google Shopping Campaigns</h4>
              <p>Product feed setup, Google Merchant Center account, and Shopping campaigns targeting jewellery searches across Gujarat. Separate campaigns for gold, diamond, and gemstone categories.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📱</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Instagram Shopping Setup</h4>
              <p>Facebook Commerce Manager configuration, product catalogue sync with Instagram, and Shopping tags added to all product posts and reels. Direct checkout enabled for Indian buyers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Local SEO for Surat Jewellery Market</h4>
              <p>Google Business Profile rebuilt with full product listings, 30+ photos, and Q&amp;A entries. Optimised for "gold jewellery Surat," "diamond jewellery Ring Road," and 15 related local keywords.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Monthly Performance Reporting</h4>
              <p>Custom Google Analytics 4 dashboard tracking revenue by product category, ad spend vs. revenue ratio, conversion rate by traffic source, and top-performing products each month.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  RESULTS (dark bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label light">The Results</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:white;">Numbers That Speak for Themselves</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">Measured at the 4-month mark. Revenue and order data verified via Shopify Analytics. Search rankings via Google Search Console.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-results-grid">
      <div class="cs-result-card cs-result-accent">
        <div class="cs-result-number">₹15L</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Monthly Revenue</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Consistent monthly revenue from the Shopify store by month 4. Starting from zero in month 1.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-card">
        <div class="cs-result-number">2.5%</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Conversion Rate</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Industry average for jewellery e-commerce is 1.2%. Gujarat Gems achieved more than double at 2.5%.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-card">
        <div class="cs-result-number">4,200</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Monthly Sessions</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Monthly organic and paid sessions combined. 38% of traffic from Google Shopping, 29% from organic search.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-card">
        <div class="cs-result-number">#1</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Local Search Ranking</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Ranking first for "gold jewellery Ring Road Surat" and top 3 for 8 other high-intent jewellery keywords in Surat.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-card cs-result-accent">
        <div class="cs-result-number">180+</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Orders per Month</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Average 180 orders per month by month 4. Average order value: Rs. 8,300. Mix of ornaments and loose gemstones.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-card">
        <div class="cs-result-number">4.7★</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">Google Review Rating</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">Post-purchase review request flow added. Google rating grew from 3.9 to 4.7 with 140+ new verified reviews.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


